{
  "stem": "5471.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was strange, strange world.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] During the day, they could talk all over the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They could talk all over the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- but everyone had a job to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They worked in the [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] joinery or [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] metal industry or-- they had several industries going there-- clothes making.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Then you had the children and the schools.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and that was all done by the Jews itself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No German interfered there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was all done, done by the Jews itself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know if they had a council.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They had Schlesinger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Schlesinger had several people working under him-- one for housing, and one for industry, and one for-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and a lot of doctors working.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Spanier, he was the head of the hospital business.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, Nelly, mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do-- were you treated in the hospital at all or by their doctors?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to Spanier every fortnight or-- and when I was close to the delivery of the baby, he said to me, Mrs. van As, please, please get out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you get the baby here, I have a chance to be deported.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Get out of here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to a hospital in Assen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And three days later, the baby was born.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he was so nervous that I would get it in the camp, I wasn't allowed to be there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were all Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I wasn't allowed to be there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that-- Why would he be in trouble?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that he hadn't taken care of-- that I was out of it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was-- was he only allowed to treat Jews?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No-- only for Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
